Class ProgramClassWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • proguard.classfile.io.ProgramClassWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AttributeVisitor, ConstantVisitor, ClassVisitor, MemberVisitor

    public class ProgramClassWriter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClassVisitor, MemberVisitor, ConstantVisitor, AttributeVisitor
    This ClassVisitor writes out the ProgramClass instances that it visits to the given DataOutput object.
